r camper van? Grab these Black Friday deals from EcoFlow on their quick-charging, high-powered portable power stations.</p><p>From smaller car-camping backup power to full home battery kits (that are a great plug-and-play solution for off-grid adventure vehicles, BTW), here’s what’s on sale now…</p><h3><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-river-pro-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow RIVER Pro</a></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator.jpg\" alt=\"ecoflow river pro battery backup generator for outdoor events and car camping\" width=\"1600\" height=\"824\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator-297x153.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator-800x412.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator-120x62.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator-768x396.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/02121053/EcoFlow-RIVER-Pro-portable-battery-powered-generator-1536x791.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The<strong> <a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-river-pro-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow RIVER Pro</a></strong> might look small, but it packs a massive 720Wh of battery capacity, making it the perfect portable companion for off-grid adventures. Keep up to 10 devices powered on at once and recharge it directly from your car (~8 hrs), solar panels (4-8 hrs), or standard AC outlets (just 96 mins!). MSRP is $649, <em><strong>Sale Price is $579</strong></em>.<br></p><h3><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-delta-mini-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow DELTA mini</a></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg\" alt=\"ecoflow delta mini battery backup solar generator for car camping and remote working\" width=\"1600\" height=\"718\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-297x133.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-800x359.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-120x54.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-768x345.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26140455/EcoFlow-DELTA-mini-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-1536x689.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Dubbed their “Prosumer Backup Power” solution, the DELTA mini’s 882Wh capacity is perfect for short power outages, outdoor adventures, and fieldwork. The <strong><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-delta-mini-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DELTA mini</a></strong> snags up to 300W from solar panels for a full recharge in 3 to 6 hours (depending on light conditions), and go from 0-100% in just 96 minutes when charging from the wall. MSRP is $999, <strong><em>Sale Price is $849</em></strong>.<br></p><h3><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-delta-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow DELTA</a></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg\" alt=\"ecoflow delta battery backup solar generator for car camping and overland vehicles\" width=\"1400\" height=\"761\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg 1400w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-297x161.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-800x435.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-120x65.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141049/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-768x417.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"></a></p><p>The standard <strong><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-delta-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DELTA</a></strong> is their essential power backup solution, giving you a huge 1260Wh capacity that’s perfect for keeping small electronics running during power outages. Or bring it along on outdoor adventures or fieldwork to power up to 13 devices simultaneously. It’ll recharge from 0% to 100% in 1.6 hours, which is 10x the speed of most portable power stations in the market. MSRP is $1,399, <em><strong>Sale Price is $1,099</strong></em>.<br></p><h3><strong><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/delta-max-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow DELTA Max</a></strong></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg\" alt=\"ecoflow delta max battery backup solar generator for car camping and remote working\" width=\"1400\" height=\"607\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator.jpg 1400w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-297x129.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-800x347.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-120x52.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141342/EcoFlow-DELTA-Max-battery-power-pack-solar-generator-768x333.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"></a></p><p>Their “Home Backup Power Master”, a single <strong><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/delta-max-portable-power-station?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow DELTA Max</a> </strong>unit packs 2kWh capacity that’s expandable up to 6kWh with DELTA Max Smart Extra Batteries. That’s enough to power your full-size home fridge and house lights for hours during a blackout. With EcoFlow’s X-Boost technology, DELTA Max can power heavy-duty devices (think, power tools) up to 3400W, making it great on job sites, too (or for blenders and microwaves in your camper van). When you do have power, the DELTA Max charges up safely and rapidly from 0-80% in just 65 minutes. MSRP is $2,099, <em><strong>Sale Price is $1,899</strong></em>.<br></p><h3><a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/products/ecoflow-delta-160w-solar-panel?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DELTA Bundle (EcoFlow DELTA + two 160W Solar Panels)</a></h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels.jpg\" alt=\"ecoflow delta battery backup power pack with solar panels to recharge it\" width=\"1400\" height=\"756\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels.jpg 1400w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels-297x160.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels-800x432.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels-120x65.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/26141836/EcoFlow-DELTA-battery-power-pack-bundle-with-solar-panels-768x415.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"></a></p><p>Combine the DELTA Portable Power station with two of EcoFlow’s 160W Solar Panels and you have a truly portable, completely off-grid solution for remote power…or prolonged outages at home or work. Their solar panels have a high conversion efficiency of 21-22%, and with two of them plugged into the EcoFlow DELTA Portable Power station it can be fully recharged in 5 to 10 hours, even in cold or partly cloudy conditions! MSRP is $2,299, <em><strong>Sale Price is $1,749</strong></em>.<br></p><hr><p><em>Disclosure: This post is sponsored by<strong> <a href=\"https://ecoflow.com/?ctc=brsptechgeneralecoflowbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EcoFlow</a>.</strong> These sales will begin on November 15.</em></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Sponsored Post","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e2399276e7e4339dd287a91665ded80dcf1b451511e42db78847c2285323d9d5","category":"Cycling"}